{"author":"RebarBotNava","data":{"alias":"hominine-stoic-eeve","description":"## Context\nStamp denormalized author name+email on every event (git-style) and an optional `author_id` referencing an identity, without breaking replay of existing events.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] Every mutating event carries denormalized author name + email; an optional `author_id` references an identity.\n- [ ] Regression test: existing events without `author_id`/email still replay to the same state.\n- [ ] `_seam.py` author resolution stamps the fields at the single locked write seam.","id":"4e9d-6d8d-c7d9-45e3","parent_id":"e68d-b701-4dd9-47aa","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"story","title":"identity: event attribution (name+email + optional author_id) + replay back-compat"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1783735866479059001,"uuid":"5bfb1122-ff64-4060-8734-b5e4826c51a8"}